    dc:date "2013" ;
    dc:title "A review of Paroplitis (Braconidae, Microgastrinae), and description of a new genus from New Zealand, Shireplitis, with convergent morphological traits" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248312>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248313>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.248314> ;
